st = ''
k_len = 13

num_k = len(st) - k_len + 1
number = 0
my_dictionary = {}

def do_work(s,n):
    for x in range (num_k):
        w = s[x:x+n]
        my_dictionary[w] = my_dictionary.get(w, 0)+1
    number = max(my_dictionary.values())

    answer = [i[0] for i in my_dictionary.items() if i[1] == number]
    return ' '.join(answer)

a = do_work(st, k_len)
print(a)
